<p>Thank you for considering a gift to LifeChurch.tv. As a reminder, all 2014 year-end gifts must be received at a campus, online, or postmarked by Wednesday, December 31.</p>

<p>Taking action on your generosity is simple. <a href="/giving/">Find out how to give at LifeChurch.tv.</a></p>

<p>Questions? Contact the Giving Team at <a href="mailto:giving@lifechurch.tv">giving@lifechurch.tv</a> or (405) 216-7054.</p>

<h2 id="what-happens-to-the-money-we-give">What happens to the money we give?</h2>

<p>God provides for the ministry of LifeChurch.tv through your tithes and offerings. We honor your gifts with faithful stewardship, ethical business practices, and full accountability so that the financial integrity of LifeChurch.tv remains beyond reproach.</p>

<p>LifeChurch.tv is accredited by the <a href="http://www.ecfa.org" target="_blank">Evangelical Council for Financial Accountability<i class="icon icon-window"></i></a>, which requires high standards of biblical accountability, board governance, financial transparency, integrity in fund raising, and proper use of charity resources. For detailed financial information, view our financial statements. For general questions about our financial practices, contact <a href="mailto:giving@lifechurch.tv">giving@lifechurch.tv</a>.</p>

